Sentencas: Fibrous Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta-Gd0.2Ce0.9O1.95 (BSCF-GDC) composite cathodes are fabricated by a facile electrospinning method.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: However, the electropun BSCF-GDC cathode shows poor adhesion to a GDC electrolyte because of the high shrinkage rate of the electrospun BSCF-GDC cathode during sintering.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: To solve this adhesion issue, mixed BSCF fiber-GDC powder cathode is investigated.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: As a result, mixed BSCF fiber-GDC powder cathode with an enhanced adhesion is successfully fabricated.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: This improvement can be attributed to the modified microstructure with the GDC powder that joins the BSCF fibers to the GDC electrolyte at the cathode and electrolyte interface.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: The polarization resistance of the mixed BSCF fiber-GDC powder cathode is 0.10 Omega cm(2), which is lower than 0.13 Omega cm(2) of conventional BSCF-GDC powder cathode at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: It is attributable to the improved oxygen gas and lattice oxygen diffusion, and the surface exchange of the mixed BSCF fiber-GDC powder cathode.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion

Sentencas: The single cell with a mixed BSCF fiber-GDC powder cathode show 500 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C, which is 25% higher than conventional BSCF-GDC powder cathode.
Titulo: Investigation of electrospun Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 cathodes for enhanced interfacial adhesion
